  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to reliance on a single test condition. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support pre-market submissions for posterior spinal fixation systems, informing load-bearing predictions for patient-specific implant sizing. All 13 credibility factors are documented herein under the Minimal profile; structured scope declaration is addressed in supplementary project documentation.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-performance-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v1",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab-a-n6-experimental",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab-b-n5-experimental"
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-f1717-ensemble-comparison-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "FEA ensemble vs. N=11 experimental F1717 compression-bending constructs"
    }
  ],
  "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4042170",
